1. mudar as teclas para | e \

xmodmap -e "keycode 10 = 1 exclam 1 exclam bar exclamdown bar"
xmodmap -e "keycode 11 = 2 at 2 at backslash onehalf backslash"

2. Tornar permanente:

nano ~/.Xmodmap

keycode 10 = 1 exclam 1 exclam bar exclamdown bar
keycode 11 = 2 at 2 at backslash onehalf backslash

3. Carregar

xmodmap ~/.Xmodmap

4. Carregar sempre e logar:

echo 'xmodmap ~/.Xmodmap' >> ~/.profile

5. Verificação (mapa):

xmodmap -pke | egrep "keycode *10|keycode *11"




